@startuml
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

skinparam actor {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #E2EFDA
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam boundary {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #B4C7E7
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam control {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #FFD966
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam entity {
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #F4B084
  FontSize 13
}

skinparam note {
  BorderColor gray
  BackgroundColor #FFFFA0
  FontSize 12
}

skinparam ranksep 80
skinparam nodesep 80

actor 用户 as User

boundary "商品详情页面" as ProductDetail
boundary "购物车页面" as CartPage

control "购物车控制器" as CartController
control "购物车服务" as CartService

entity "购物车" as Cart
entity "购物车项" as CartItem
entity "商品" as Product

User -down-> ProductDetail : 浏览
User -down-> CartPage : 访问

ProductDetail -right-> CartController : 加入购物车
CartPage -right-> CartController : 修改/删除购物车

CartController -down-> CartService : 调用
CartService -down-> Cart : 操作
CartService -right-> CartItem : 操作
CartService -left-> Product : 引用

note bottom of ProductDetail : 添加商品到购物车
note bottom of CartPage : 管理购物车项
note bottom of CartController : 处理购物车操作\n检查库存状态
note bottom of CartService : 实现购物车业务逻辑
@enduml